### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@painterToken = YOUR_PAINTER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Availability (Painter only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2025-10-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-15T17:00:00Z"
}

### Create Another Availability Slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

{
  "startTime": "2025-10-16T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-16T16:00:00Z"
}

### Get My Availability (Painter only)
# Note: Response includes nested bookings for each availability slot
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/me
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

### Get My Availability with Pagination - Page 1
# Returns 5 availability slots per page, each with its associated bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/me?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

### Get My Availability with Pagination - Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/me?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

### Get My Availability with Custom Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/availability/me?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

### Try with overlapping time (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/availability
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{painterToken}}

